high_descs: Turn left and go to the left cabinet above the stove and the microwave
Take out the gray bowl from the cabinet.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator on the right across the kitchen
Chill the gray bowl in the refrigerator and take it out.
Turn around and go to the front of the green table.
Place the gray bowl on the left side of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl on the table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk forward and look up to face the cabinet above the microwave.
Pick up the bowl from the cabinet above the microwave.
Turn around and walk across the room and turn to the right to face fridge on the right.
Cool the bowl in the fridge and then remove it.
Turn around and step forward to face the table in the center of the room.
Place the bowl on the table in the center of the room.
anns.task_desc: To cool a bowl as well as place it on the center table.

high_descs: Go to the cupboard above the microwave
Take a bowl out of the cupboard
Chill the bowl in the fridge
Put the bowl on the table
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl on a table
